The paper deals with the problem of matrix completion, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. The use of stochastic gradient descent and the focus on efficiency suggest that the paper is likely to be in the cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories. The combinatorial nature of the problem and the use of optimization techniques suggest that cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also possible sub-categories.
